Section: ruby
Priority: extra
Homepage: http://red-e.eu/app/salor-hospitality/
Description: The innovative Point of Sale Solution serving the Hospitality Industry
 This package consists of a lean Ruby-on-Rails application, backed from a
 MySQL database. The actual Point of Sale interface is entirely controlled
 by offline Javascript and an offline database. This concept unites the
 advantages of networking between many handhelds in one store (or many
 stores of a restaurant/hotel chain) with an amazing responsiveness of the
 user interface (UI).
